  "short_description": "Inspired by the most epic and little known battle of the Great War, Haunted: Attack of the Dead Men puts you in the middle of a chaotic fight for your life against hundreds of resurrected Russians. Put your arsenal of 8 weapons to good use through 14 levels as you rid the world of this nightmare...",
