  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/cd65f7af577a1726b5f7d0c7f53ceaf2.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span>Enter Osowiec, one of the most formidable fortresses in Europe during the Great War.  It's defenders have been through hell - trench warfare, a barrage of artillery, gas - and have returned.  The fortress now serves as the source of a great darkness, returning the dead to the land of the living.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/18fbba95e95053b2e8fb0077dd8cbe8c.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a lone German soldier in the heat of the epic ​battle for this fortress, <i>The Attack of the Dead Men</i>.  Your comrades have abandoned you and fled in disgrace, and now you are all alone, trapped in Osowiec, surrounded by hundreds of undead, angry Russians.  Battle for survival against the hordes, and put them down once again for good to prevent the darkness from spreading over all of Europe...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/8238f201780b3c0ddbf183b3bea0c104.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is only one path to victory - be the last man standing, dead or alive.  Utilise a vast array of weapons to dispatch your foes and conquer this evil place as a one-man army.  Many of the weapons in your arsenal enjoy alternate fire modes to ensure that this monumental task is executed with peak German efficiency... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/c19e66fa04725cb5530cedaa808506f9.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The odds are truly stacked against you.  Reaching the source of this great evil requires a methodical cleansing of the entire fortress complex.  You will need everything you've got to deal with the increasing number of undead, who get stronger and more resilient the deeper you go...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/7171f7837eb0d66ff406f558e95f3b5f.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7+ hour single-player campaign in the style of first-person shooters of old</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purist boomer shooter gameplay - that means no reloading, no checkpoints, and absolutely no wall jumping, bunny hopping or other fancy-ass movement mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 levels in the main campaign + a secret level (the first 4 levels are available to play in the demo right now!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 choices of weapon (+ alternate fire modes for many) to dispatch the multitude of undead</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 difficulty levels + 3 bonus difficulties that unlock upon completing the game on the hardest difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense encounters with dozens of enemies all at once throughout the campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn rewards for more aggressive play-styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete to achieve the best score in each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different types of enemy, all with unique attack patterns and fighting styles, to keep the action engaging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic boss battle against a well known Russian mystic who has now been dabbling in necromancy...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/b43a2858f5fe0b39dca7909db7cc0ca5.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/cd65f7af577a1726b5f7d0c7f53ceaf2.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span>Enter Osowiec, one of the most formidable fortresses in Europe during the Great War.  It's defenders have been through hell - trench warfare, a barrage of artillery, gas - and have returned.  The fortress now serves as the source of a great darkness, returning the dead to the land of the living.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/18fbba95e95053b2e8fb0077dd8cbe8c.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a lone German soldier in the heat of the epic ​battle for this fortress, <i>The Attack of the Dead Men</i>.  Your comrades have abandoned you and fled in disgrace, and now you are all alone, trapped in Osowiec, surrounded by hundreds of undead, angry Russians.  Battle for survival against the hordes, and put them down once again for good to prevent the darkness from spreading over all of Europe...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/8238f201780b3c0ddbf183b3bea0c104.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/925fbf6f68e4269974a8b08677beacfc.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is only one path to victory - be the last man standing, dead or alive.  Utilise a vast array of weapons to dispatch your foes and conquer this evil place as a one-man army.  Many of the weapons in your arsenal enjoy alternate fire modes to ensure that this monumental task is executed with peak German efficiency... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/0132b4003925b80a64b593ad1b341cfe.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/c19e66fa04725cb5530cedaa808506f9.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.poster.avif?t=1758303544\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.webm?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/4ecb016ac451bfba2aafc14c3002fa3f.mp4?t=1758303544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The odds are truly stacked against you.  Reaching the source of this great evil requires a methodical cleansing of the entire fortress complex.  You will need everything you've got to deal with the increasing number of undead, who get stronger and more resilient the deeper you go...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157920/extras/7171f7837eb0d66ff406f558e95f3b5f.avif?t=1758303544\" width=600 height=96 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7+ hour single-player campaign in the style of first-person shooters of old</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purist boomer shooter gameplay - that means no reloading, no checkpoints, and absolutely no wall jumping, bunny hopping or other fancy-ass movement mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 levels in the main campaign + a secret level (the first 4 levels are available to play in the demo right now!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 choices of weapon (+ alternate fire modes for many) to dispatch the multitude of undead</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 difficulty levels + 3 bonus difficulties that unlock upon completing the game on the hardest difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense encounters with dozens of enemies all at once throughout the campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn rewards for more aggressive play-styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete to achieve the best score in each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different types of enemy, all with unique attack patterns and fighting styles, to keep the action engaging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic boss battle against a well known Russian mystic who has now been dabbling in necromancy...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li></ul>",
